# About us

Intema Group is a Russian distributor of materials for foundry production. Since 2014 we have been supplying binder systems, release coatings, and auxiliary products to leading aluminium, iron, and steel facilities.

## Our method

1. Study the customer process and run lab tests on sand and coatings.
2. Fine-tune formulations, prepare application guidelines, and document safety rules.
3. Supervise the plant start-up and provide 24/7 technical support.

{% alert tone="warning" title="Quality assurance" %}
Every shipment includes a certificate of analysis. We record strength, permeability, and coating parameters before dispatch.
{% /alert %}

